Package: jointest
Version: 2.0
Date: 2024-11-15
Title: Multivariate Testing Through Joint Resampling-Based Tests
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Livio", "Finos", email = "livio.finos@unipd.it", role = c("cre","aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3181-8078")),
    person("Angela", "Andreella", role = "aut"),
    person("Filippo", "Gambarota", role = "ctb"))
Description: Runs resampling-based tests jointly (e.g., sign-flip score tests <doi:10.1111/rssb.12369>) to allow for multivariate testing, i.e., weak and strong control of the Familywise Error Rate or True Discovery Proportion.
